- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The UAVs are used to monitor and track the development of a wildfire, which requires computer vision techniques such as object detection and tracking. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a control framework for a team of UAVs, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
